  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "59d7a3f19d071300121ea0d2",
      "text": "破壊的イノベーション",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507304492,
      "updated": 1507304496
    },
    {
      "id": "5a598384aff09e0000a74c47",
      "text": "クリステンセンらにより「性能の劣った製品が市場のシェアを奪う事例」が報告された。 (=破壊的イノベーション)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1515815813,
      "updated": 1515815819
    },
    {
      "id": "5a598384aff09e0000a74c4a",
      "text": "例えば、 HDDにおいては容量の少ない製品が容量の多い製品を駆逐した。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1515815813,
      "updated": 1515815822
    },
    {
      "id": "5a598384aff09e0000a74c4c",
      "text": "* Clayton M. Christensen, Joseph L. Bower (1996) “Customer power, strategic investment, and the",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1515815813,
      "updated": 1515815813
    },
    {
      "id": "5a598384aff09e0000a74c4d",
      "text": "failure of leading firms.” Strategic Management Journal",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1515815813,
      "updated": 1515815813
    },
    {
      "id": "5a598383aff09e0000a74c46",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1515815812,
      "updated": 1515815812
    },
    {
      "id": "59d7a437aff09e00008520bb",
